data.description:
This lovely 3 bedroom, loft and 2.5 bath home is located in Peoria. Don't miss out on this move in ready home with NEW carpet and New interior paint throughout! This home has been well cared for by the original owners. This home is situated on a premium lot siding to the wash, corner lot & NO neighbors behind. Water-efficient front desert landscaping. Spacious family room with vaulted ceiling and natural light adjacent to the kitchen. The kitchen is well-equipped with maple cabinetry, a walk-in pantry, KitchenAid refrigerator, gas stove, and a nice size island with seating. This could be a great space for cooking and entertaining. All bedrooms, laundry room and loft are located upstairs. Huge primary suite with walk in closet, private water closet, dual sinks, separate tub & shower. The secondary bedrooms are all nice size with ceiling fans.

Backyard is a private retreat including a covered patio, storage shed and real grass (just think what Winter grass will look like). Home is near community park and is near walking trails! Just the right distance from the 101, Arrowhead Mall, P83 Entertainment District with AZ Ice, restaurants, movies and so much more.
